          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Modelling: \n•\nData collection,\n•\nData cleaning,\n•\nPreprocessing,\n•\nFeature \nExtraction,\n•\nModelling,\n•\nEvaluation\n•\nDeployment",
          "bbox": [
